    {
      "id": "36",
      "name": "相關訊息",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "人物關係",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "莫索·郎勃罗梭",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "科學家，三十年前創造了「曲線」。他想要創造一台通過理解謊言，理解人類，進而成為人類的機器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4722,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Talochard",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 5223,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/26/237301566/615412682c0d3edc7483b9452030aa64_4315552892343881539.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Marechaussee Phantom",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "的證物保管員，在證據室發現了「曲線」。她想幫他打破「莫索協議」，成為一個真正的「人」。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "相關物品",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
